video.title: Marvel's Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.
video.synopsis: Agent Phil Coulson, seen in action in Marvel's The Avengers, assembles a team of top S.H.I.E.L.D. agents to investigate bizarre threats.

episodes.synopsis: To track an unknown enemy, agent Phil Coulson assembles a select group of agents from the worldwide law-enforcement organization known as S.H.I.E.L.D.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: Coulson runs into Comandante Camilla Reyes when he and the agents travel to Peru to investigate a mysterious object.
When brilliant scientist Dr. Franklin Hall is kidnapped, Agent Coulson and his S.H.I.E.L.D. team must race against the clock to locate him.
episodes.title: The Asset

episodes.synopsis: Agent Coulson and the team track down a mysterious woman who has single-handedly committed numerous high-stakes heists.
episodes.title: Eye Spy

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and the team try to rescue a young man with an unusual and dangerous power. Skye has a secret that jeopardizes her relationship with the team.
episodes.title: Girl in the Flower Dress

episodes.synopsis: When floating bodies turn up, Coulson and the agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. must hunt down an elusive killer. No one is safe -- not even the team.
episodes.title: F.Z.Z.T

episodes.synopsis: Agent Coulson works the system to save Ward and Fitz when they're sent on a Level 8 classified mission.
episodes.title: The Hub

episodes.synopsis: In the aftermath of the events chronicled in the feature film Thor: The Dark World, Coulson and the S.H.I.E.L.D. team try to pick up the pieces.
episodes.title: The Well

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and his team are haunted by a mysterious force that threatens to destroy them all, and only a secret from May's past can save them.
episodes.title: Repairs

episodes.synopsis: In a shocking cliff-hanger, Coulson takes the war back to Centipede, and this time he brings in Mike Peterson for some supersoldier support.
episodes.title: The Bridge

episodes.synopsis: Coulson uncovers vital information about the mystery of his death, but with Centipede out for blood, the knowledge may come at a great cost.
episodes.title: The Magical Place

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and May uncover startling information about Skye's past, while the team is swept into a storm at S.H.I.E.L.D. Academy.
episodes.title: Seeds

episodes.synopsis: Hot on the trail of the Clairvoyant, Coulson and his team board a mystery train that seems headed for certain death.
episodes.title: T.R.A.C.K.S.

episodes.synopsis: On a quest to save Skye, Coulson enlists the aid of Ward's former supervising officer -- and uncovers shocking truths about himself and S.H.I.E.L.D.
episodes.title: T.A.H.I.T.I.

episodes.synopsis: When deadly seductress Lorelei attacks Coulson and his team, Thor's Lady Sif, Lorelei's longtime nemesis, steps in to try to save them.
episodes.title: Yes Men

episodes.synopsis: Agents Garrett and Triplett are back to help Coulson's team track down S.H.I.E.L.D.'s nefarious enemy -- the Clairvoyant.
episodes.title: End of the Beginning

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and his team find themselves without anyone they can trust, only to discover that they're trapped with a traitor in their midst.
episodes.title: Turn, Turn, Turn

episodes.synopsis: With Col. Glenn Talbot now on their trail, Coulson and his team take refuge and begin to uncover S.H.I.E.L.D.'s most dangerous secrets.
episodes.title: Providence

episodes.synopsis: When the life of Coulson's true love is threatened by Hydra, the team must undertake a perilous mission to save her.
episodes.title: The Only Light in the Darkness

episodes.synopsis: Agent Maria Hill returns to help Coulson as what's left of S.H.I.E.L.D. collapses due to the efforts of Hydra.
episodes.title: Nothing Personal

episodes.synopsis: While Ward recalls his first time meeting Garrett, Coulson and May infiltrate Cybertek and uncover details about Garrett’s past in Project Deathlok.
episodes.title: Ragtag

episodes.synopsis: With his team severely debilitated, Coulson pulls out all the stops to put an end to Garrett and the forces of Hydra.
episodes.title: Beginning of the End

episodes.synopsis: As Fitz's mental issues worsen, Coulson sends Skye and other S.H.I.E.L.D. agents to retrieve the Obelisk, a Hydra weapon stolen during World War II.
episodes.title: Shadows

episodes.synopsis: General Talbot captures Hunter, then offers him a deal to betray Coulson, while May pursues Creel, who has absorbed the Obelisk's deadly powers.
episodes.title: Heavy Is the Head

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and his team compete with Hydra to recruit Gill, a volatile gifted with cryokinetic skills, and the loyalty of Hydra mole Simmons is tested.
episodes.title: Making Friends and Influencing People

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and Talbot vie to acquire an ancient church painting with mysterious engravings, while Agent May pursues brainwashed Hydra spy Agent 33.
episodes.title: Face My Enemy

episodes.synopsis: Raina sees Simmons contacting Coulson about the Obelisk, now controlled by "The Doctor," and threatens to expose her unless Coulson offers protection.
episodes.title: A Hen in the Wolf House

episodes.synopsis: S.H.I.E.L.D.'s future is in question after Hydra mercenaries impersonate them to attack the United Nations and Senator Ward orders an investigation.
episodes.title: A Fractured House

episodes.synopsis: When an unstable man starts murdering former S.H.I.E.L.D. agents and carving alien glyphs on them, Coulson seeks answers in Hydra's memory machine.
episodes.title: The Writing on the Wall

episodes.synopsis: To reclaim the Obelisk, Coulson and the team dig into Hydra's evil past, while Ward kidnaps his brother and confronts him about a childhood secret.
episodes.title: The Things We Bury

episodes.synopsis: Half of Coulson's team undertakes a frantic search for the alien city's entrance while the other half risks all to rescue Raina from Hydra's clutches.
episodes.title: Ye Who Enter Here

episodes.synopsis: Once inside, S.H.I.E.L.D. agents race to destroy the alien city before Hydra can lay claim to it. Skye uncovers a shocking secret about her past.
episodes.title: What They Become

episodes.synopsis: After Whitehall's death, Hydra vows revenge against Coulson, while Skye tries to cope with the aftereffects of her newfound earthquake abilities.
episodes.title: Aftershocks

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and team help Lady Sif, who lost her memory after fighting a mysterious warrior, while Bobbi and Mack plot their next secret moves.
episodes.title: Who You Really Are

episodes.synopsis: To destroy S.H.I.E.L.D., Cal gathers its enemies to form a team of supervillains. May asks her therapist ex-husband to help Skye control her gift.
episodes.title: One of Us

episodes.synopsis: With Ward's help, Agent 33 tries to undo Whitehall's alterations, while Bobbi and Mack reveal their allegiance to Hunter and the "real S.H.I.E.L.D."
episodes.title: Love in the Time of Hydra

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and the team confront Bobbi and Mack about their allegiances, and a still-struggling Skye gets advice from a strange but powerful source.
episodes.title: One Door Closes

episodes.synopsis: Loyalties are tested when Gonzales insists that the Fury toolbox be opened. Skye learns more about her powers from Inhuman transitioner Lincoln.
episodes.title: Afterlife

episodes.synopsis: Caught between S.H.I.E.LD. factions, May reflects on her troubled history with Coulson, and Skye makes a startling discovery about her heritage.
episodes.title: Melinda

episodes.synopsis: Desperate to infiltrate Hydra, Coulson and Hunter offer the captured Ward a deal, while Skye finds herself trapped between her warring parents.
episodes.title: Frenemy of My Enemy

episodes.synopsis: With help from Bakshi, Coulson leads a team into the Hydra base. To save Lincoln, as foreseen by Raina, Gordon guides Skye back to S.H.I.E.L.D.
episodes.title: The Dirty Half Dozen

episodes.synopsis: Thanks to Coulson's world-saving helicarrier, the S.H.I.E.L.D. factions unite, but tensions between Skye's mother and Gonzales come to a brutal head.
episodes.title: Scars

episodes.synopsis: Jiaying convinces Skye and the Inhumans to fight against S.H.I.E.L.D., but Coulson sees through her deception and plots to save Skye and her father.
episodes.title: S.O.S.: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Led by Jiaying, the Inhumans attack the S.H.I.E.L.D. ship, intending to kill all humans, and Coulson's team must infiltrate the ship to stop them.
episodes.title: S.O.S.: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and S.H.I.E.L.D. discover the existence of a rival organization that also seeks Inhumans. Fitz takes drastic steps to find Simmons.
episodes.title: Laws of Nature

episodes.synopsis: Fitz and the team enlist an Asgardian to unlock the monolith's secrets. Lance hunts for Ward, who is rebuilding Hydra. May reaches a crossroads.
episodes.title: Purpose In the Machine

episodes.synopsis: Daisy, Mack and Coulson help Lincoln as he flees from Rosalind and the ATCU. Lance plots the infiltration of Hydra. Fitz helps Simmons readjust.
episodes.title: A Wanted (Inhu) Man

episodes.synopsis: Coulson makes an agreement with Rosalind. The agents pursue Lash, an Inhuman killing others of his kind. Lance prepares to meet in person with Ward.
episodes.title: Devils You Know

episodes.synopsis: Simmons recounts the story of her time on Maveth, the inhospitable alien world where she was a castaway, and the mysterious stranger who saved her.
episodes.title: 4,722 Hours

episodes.synopsis: May returns to duty and enlists Bobbi to go after Ward and Hydra. Daisy and Coulson suspect that ATCU's second-in-command, Banks, has a secret.
episodes.title: Among Us Hide...

episodes.synopsis: May learns the truth about Andrew. Fitz retrieves information from Simmons's phone that could save Will. Daisy and Rosalind tour the "Zephyr One."
episodes.title: Chaos Theory

episodes.synopsis: Coulson uses his growing relationship with Rosalind to uncover the truth about ATCU's plans for the Inhumans. Ward learns the real purpose of Hydra.
episodes.title: Many Heads, One Tale

episodes.synopsis: Coulson vows revenge after a devastating attack. Fitz and Simmons are taken captive by Ward's forces and prepped to travel through the portal.
episodes.title: Closure

episodes.synopsis: The forces of S.H.I.E.L.D. and Hydra clash both on Earth and the distant world of Maveth, where a final reckoning unfolds between Coulson and Ward.
episodes.title: Maveth

episodes.synopsis: After meeting with President Ellis, Coulson's more determined than ever to defeat Hydra. Daisy and the team discover more Inhumans with unique powers.
episodes.title: Bouncing Back

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and General Talbot attend an international conference about Inhumans where they discover that Gideon Malick has planted a spy in their midst.
episodes.title: The Inside Man

episodes.synopsis: On the trail of Gideon Malick, Bobbi and Lance travel to Russia and become embroiled in an assassination and coup plot, threatening their lives.
episodes.title: Parting Shot

episodes.synopsis: A group called the Watchdogs emerges to wipe out Inhumans, but the team traces its true origins. Simmons discovers an important chemical compound.
episodes.title: Watchdogs

episodes.synopsis: Thanks to a momentary touch by an Inhuman, Daisy glimpses a dark future. Hive wipes out a corporate board. May must bid Andrew farewell.
episodes.title: Spacetime

episodes.synopsis: Hive calls a meeting of Hydra leadership to reveal his true self and teaches Gideon a lesson in loyalty. Daisy reveals more of her future vision.
episodes.title: Paradise Lost

episodes.synopsis: Daisy sends the Secret Warriors on their first mission: rescuing Coulson and his team from Hydra. The agents discover a traitor among them.
episodes.title: The Team

episodes.synopsis: Fitz, Simmons and Mack seek out a transhumanist scientist who may know how to stop Hive. An injured Coulson tries to rescue Daisy.
episodes.title: The Singularity

episodes.synopsis: Hive's sinister plan for humanity is revealed, while Coulson and a strike team move to stop him. Lincoln volunteers to take a risky antitoxin.
episodes.title: Failed Experiments

episodes.synopsis: Events move closer to fulfilling Daisy's tragic future vision as the Sokovia Accords go into effect, forcing the registration of all Inhumans.
episodes.title: Emancipation

episodes.synopsis: The final showdown between S.H.I.E.L.D. and Hive begins as the clock ticks down toward a devastating missile launch. Daisy is wracked with guilt.
episodes.title: Absolution

episodes.synopsis: As the war between Hive and humanity comes to an epic conclusion, one S.H.I.E.L.D. team member makes the ultimate sacrifice to save the world.
episodes.title: Ascension

episodes.synopsis: Coulson joins forces with Mack to track down Inhumans, May steps into a new role, and Ghost Rider makes a fiery first impression on Daisy.
episodes.title: The Ghost

episodes.synopsis: Coulson gets to know the new boss while Daisy bites off more than she can chew. May's problems multiply as she grows increasingly paranoid.
episodes.title: Meet the New Boss

episodes.synopsis: Coulson, Mack and Fitz pursue a rogue group with a sinister agenda. Elsewhere, blackouts hit multiple cities, and Mace tries to calm the public.
episodes.title: Uprising

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and Mack seek help from an unlikely ally. Ghost Rider's quest for revenge takes an explosive turn. Daisy tracks the Watchdogs.
episodes.title: Let Me Stand Next to Your Fire

episodes.synopsis: The Ghost Rider threatens to overpower Robbie. S.H.I.E.L.D. takes on a new mission inside a prison. Mace makes a deal.
episodes.title: Lockup

episodes.synopsis: Robbie reveals the truth about how the Ghost Rider came to be. Mace sends Simmons on a secret assignment. Fitz tracks Lucy.
episodes.title: The Good Samaritan

episodes.synopsis: S.H.I.E.L.D. deals with the aftermath of a devastating loss, Ghost Rider feels the pressure, and Coulson searches for a way to get home.
episodes.title: Deals with Our Devils

episodes.synopsis: With the fate of Los Angeles at stake, Mace pulls out all the stops in the fight against Morrow. Ghost Rider and S.H.I.E.L.D. form an alliance.
episodes.title: The Laws of Inferno Dynamics

episodes.synopsis: Disturbing new developments threaten to engulf S.H.I.E.L.D, but Coulson remains in the dark. Aida searches for the Darkhold.
episodes.title: Broken Promises

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and Mack learn a shocking truth, and Mace suffers a close call. Meanwhile, Fitz starts a secretive side project.
episodes.title: The Patriot

episodes.synopsis: Daisy and Mace attend a contentious Senate hearing, Coulson and Yo-Yo are caught where they shouldn't be, and Mack opens up about his past.
episodes.title: Wake Up

episodes.synopsis: Coulson has a problem when Agent Koenig is abducted by the Watchdogs. The Radcliffe LMD faces down some aggressive questioning.
episodes.title: Hot Potato Soup

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and Mack track down the mysterious Agnes Kitsworth. Mace and Daisy search for a way to trap and contain a powerful foe.
episodes.title: Boom

episodes.synopsis: While Mace struggles to stay alive, Coulson and the Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. attempt a bold and desperate rescue.
episodes.title: The Man Behind the Shield

episodes.synopsis: LMDs are everywhere, and S.H.I.E.L.D. can no longer be sure who is real and who isn't. Later, the agents enter an alternate reality.
episodes.title: Self Control

episodes.synopsis: Within the Framework, anything can happen, including a world run by Hydra. Daisy and Simmons discover a shocking secret.
episodes.title: What If…

episodes.synopsis: Daisy and Simmons struggle to find a way back to the real world. Meanwhile, the leader of the Resistance is finally revealed.
episodes.title: Identity and Change

episodes.synopsis: Simmons reveals her history, and Coulson tries to atone for a past mistake. Mace and May engage in a battle with severe consequences.
episodes.title: No Regrets

episodes.synopsis: Daisy and May make a break for it. S.H.I.E.L.D. and Hydra engage in a war of propaganda. Simmons's investigation leads to a terrifying conclusion.
episodes.title: All the Madame's Men

episodes.synopsis: Time is running out for the Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. to escape the Framework. Simmons's visit to see Fitz's father doesn't go as planned.
episodes.title: Farewell, Cruel World!

episodes.synopsis: The team scores a victory, but the celebration is cut short. Later, Fitz makes a painful admission, and Aida gets in touch with her emotions.
episodes.title: The Return

episodes.synopsis: In the season finale, an old ally returns, Coulson and May have an awkward chat, and Ivanov announces his plans for Darkhold.
episodes.title: World's End

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and his crew wake to find themselves trapped on a spaceship, with no recollection of how they got there and no clue what to do next.
episodes.title: Orientation (Part One)

episodes.synopsis: Deke advises Coulson and company to blend in and work hard while looking for a way home -- advice that's easier said than done.
episodes.title: Orientation (Part Two)

episodes.synopsis: Simmons receives an unenviable task. Coulson continues to puzzle over Virgil's cryptic notebook while the team falls under suspicion.
episodes.title: A Life Spent

episodes.synopsis: As their captors' sinister objectives come into focus, Coulson weighs his options and questions Deke about what happens on Level 35.
episodes.title: A Life Earned

episodes.synopsis: After Coulson and company disappear from the diner, Fitz is taken into custody and begins an incredible adventure to save the team.
episodes.title: Rewind

episodes.synopsis: While the Kree push forward with their sinister plan, Coulson and the team cross paths with a powerful new ally. Simmons and Fitz share a moment.
episodes.title: Fun & Games

episodes.synopsis: With their escape plan compromised, Coulson and his team are forced to improvise. Flint faces a difficult choice. Kasius makes a move.
episodes.title: Together or Not at All

episodes.synopsis: Aboard the Zephyr, Coulson and the Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. discover that their futures depend on someone from their past.
episodes.title: The Last Day

episodes.synopsis: As Flint, Mack and Yo-Yo lead a resistance against the Kree, the gravity storm puts the Zephyr and its passengers in peril.
episodes.title: Best Laid Plans

episodes.synopsis: Facing their last chance to return to their own timeline, Coulson and his team brace for every possibility -- especially the bad ones.
episodes.title: Past Life

episodes.synopsis: Following a dangerous journey, Coulson and the Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. discover that things aren't as they remember them.
episodes.title: All the Comforts of Home

episodes.synopsis: Fitz clues Coulson and May into General Hale's plan. Later, Coulson comes clean about his agreement with Ghost Rider.
episodes.title: The Real Deal

episodes.synopsis: Alex shows off his talents with a frightening display. The team searches for gravitonium in hopes of sealing the rift.
episodes.title: Principia

episodes.synopsis: Yo-Yo grows impatient with her recovery progress. Coulson confronts General Hale. Fitz searches for an advantage against a familiar foe.
episodes.title: The Devil Complex

episodes.synopsis: General Hale's history comes into focus. Later, Coulson is faced with a momentous choice -- and neither option is appealing.
episodes.title: Rise and Shine

episodes.synopsis: Creel begins to have second thoughts after attempting to absorb the gravitonium. Simmons and Daisy struggle to see eye to eye about Fitz.
episodes.title: Inside Voices

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and Talbot trek through the mountains with Ruby close behind. Meanwhile, Daisy and the team take a calculated risk.
episodes.title: The Honeymoon

episodes.synopsis: The Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. search for a way to stop Ruby from destroying Earth -- a feat that may prove impossible.
episodes.title: All Roads Lead ...

episodes.synopsis: As Daisy and Yo-Yo argue over past decisions, Coulson strives to maintain order, and Talbot has a moment of recognition.
episodes.title: Option Two

episodes.synopsis: Coulson and a reinvigorated Talbot visit Qovas's ship for a high-stakes meeting. Mack crosses paths with an enemy that may have information.
episodes.title: The One Who Will Save Us All

episodes.synopsis: While Daisy wakes to bad news and Qovas tries to put Coulson and May in their place, Fitz and Simmons ponder a plan to save one of their own.
episodes.title: The Force of Gravity

episodes.synopsis: With Coulson's fate hanging in the balance, the rest of the agents realize that someone might need to make the ultimate sacrifice.
episodes.title: The End

episodes.synopsis: In deep space, Daisy, Simmons, Piper and Davis search for Fitz. Back on Earth, agents investigate reality distortions with Mack at the helm.
episodes.title: Missing Pieces

episodes.synopsis: With Agent May in hot pursuit, Sarge and his team commit a series of heists to obtain high-tech crystals.
episodes.title: Window of Opportunity

episodes.synopsis: On planet Kitson, the agents hit a roadblock on their interstellar mission to rescue Fitz and Enoch, who engage in high-stakes gambling.
episodes.title: Fear and Loathing on the Planet of Kitson

episodes.synopsis: The crew continues to hunt for Sarge as he seeks knowledge of S.H.I.E.L.D. and alien technology. A batlike parasite threatens Keller.
episodes.title: Code Yellow

episodes.synopsis: As an agent comes face to face with Sarge, who inquires about Coulson, Dr. Benson and the team are left puzzled by another bizarre loss.
episodes.title: The Other Thing

episodes.synopsis: Trapped in Atarah's memory prison, Fitz and Simmons confront one another's darker sides.
episodes.title: Inescapable

episodes.synopsis: With Sarge in S.H.I.E.L.D. custody, Mack and team interrogate him about his nefarious plan. Back on Kitson, a mysterious stranger assists FitzSimmons.
episodes.title: Toldja

episodes.synopsis: Unable to identify Earth's true enemy, the S.H.I.E.L.D. agents seek help from Sarge, whose cryptic intentions for the Shrike conflict with Izel's.
episodes.title: Collision Course (Part I)

episodes.synopsis: Time is running out for the Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. as they fight to rescue FitzSimmons and save the planet. Izel teases Sarge's true identity.
episodes.title: Collision Course (Part 2)

episodes.synopsis: After catching wind of a body-hopping enemy in their midst, the agents must prove to one another that they are not possessed.
episodes.title: Leap

episodes.synopsis: Izel executes a mind-bending plan to visit an ancient temple. Elsewhere, Sarge struggles to come to terms with a revealing truth about who he is.
episodes.title: From the Ashes

episodes.synopsis: After bending space and time, the agents must exhaust all efforts to stop the end of the world as Sarge and his team continue their mission.
episodes.title: The Sign

episodes.synopsis: In the epic finale, everyone's fate hangs in the balance. But when Sarge and Izel join forces, who will survive?
episodes.title: New Life

episodes.synopsis: Transported to NYC in 1931, the agents and the LMD Phil Coulson collide with Chronicoms and realize they must work fast to safeguard S.H.I.E.L.D.
episodes.title: The New Deal

episodes.synopsis: The team must protect the timeline-unraveling "thread" at all costs. But the mission ultimately leads the agents to question their own values.
episodes.title: Know Your Onions

episodes.synopsis: A surprising leap forward in time sends the agents to an unfamiliar decade where they must infiltrate one of their own bases to stop the Chronicoms.
episodes.title: Alien Commies from the Future!

episodes.synopsis: Thanks to a system glitch, Coulson realizes why July 22, 1955, is so important. Can he change history and save a life while preserving the timeline?
episodes.title: Out of the Past

episodes.synopsis: Bumping up to 1973, the agents encounter a surprise and discover a way to defeat the Chronicoms. But then the Zephyr bolts forward.
episodes.title: A Trout in the Milk

episodes.synopsis: Cover blown, the team scrambles to rescue Mack's parents, save S.H.I.E.L.D. and repair the Zephyr. Meanwhile, Nathaniel attempts a power grab.
episodes.title: Adapt or Die

episodes.synopsis: Stranded in 1982, Mack retreats to his childhood home as Deke puts together a new band — of agents. In the meantime, Sibyl takes a deadly new form.
episodes.title: The Totally Excellent Adventures of Mack and The D

episodes.synopsis: A malfunctioning Zephyr propels the team toward certain disaster. Hopes turn to Yo-Yo, but first, she must enlist the help of an old enemy.
episodes.title: After, Before

episodes.synopsis: As a time vortex traps the Zephyr, Daisy and Coulson relive their failed attempts to save the team. Who will be called upon to make a final sacrifice?
episodes.title: As I Have Always Been

episodes.synopsis: The team returns to 1983 where Nathaniel and Kora have been keeping busy. Daisy must protect Jiaying as a supercharged former nemesis enters the game.
episodes.title: Stolen

episodes.synopsis: As Kora attempts to win the team's trust, Nathaniel lays the groundwork for a dark new future. Unpredictable actions just might undo Sibyl.
episodes.title: Brand New Day

episodes.synopsis: Nathaniel and Sibyl edge closer to erasing S.H.I.E.L.D. from the history books while the agents band together in part one of a two-part series finale.
episodes.title: The End Is at Hand

episodes.synopsis: As S.H.I.E.L.D. teeters on the brink of extinction, the team reunites with old friends to try to outsmart their foes in part two of the series finale.
episodes.title: What We're Fighting For
